            <p class="mt-3" style="font-size:2rem;"><span style="font-weight:bold; color:darkblue">DEGCA</span> exist for the total development of every child in our care: spiritual, moral, intellectual, social, emotional, and physical. We have no interest in educating children merely to for good grades and employment or honorable positions. Rather, our delight is educating children to have self-identity, purpose for life, awareness of potential, leadership and moral integrity with an unwavering passion to live fulfilled life.</p>
